com.topcoder.uml.actions.project
Class GenerateCodeAction

java.lang.Object
  com.topcoder.uml.actions.project.GenerateCodeAction
All Implemented Interfaces:
com.topcoder.uml.actionmanager.Action, com.topcoder.uml.actionmanager.TransientAction
public class GenerateCodeAction
extends java.lang.Object
implements com.topcoder.uml.actionmanager.TransientAction

GenerateCodeAction class implements TransientAction interface and it will generate code for the given packages or classifiers. It will use the Stub Class Generator component to perform the actual logic.

Thread-safety: This class is immutable, and its thread-safety depends on the Stub Class Generator component.

Version:
1.0
Author:
standlove, TCSDEVELOPER
